<title>Hung Un Gel Un</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Cham ka'ng lo sel lal ahi tai,
 Theipi nah le a sel tai;
 Zie guol chun tel chuom te hawle,
 Lalpa pak cha di'n no kit un.

[V2]
 Hung un, gel un phat chieh dan hi,
 Suol a thisa thawhphat a hi tai;
 Gam hung tung ding kinem in,
 Ngak zing hitiu kisazo diem in.

[V3]
 2. Chul thei Lili pakcha haw le,
 Hun chawm khat a ding mai in;
 Gim lim takin a hung pak ui,
 Namtin lung a sukipak sek.

[V4]
 3. Zie ziek chun suohpih te hung un,
 Lal Krista chawi-an dingin;
 Gun chuh takin na sem hitiu,
 Leisiet hinkhuo a beih ma hin.

[V5]
 4. Phat lopi chuh hung mang ina,
 Gunchuh leh kinem takin;
 Hung kisau, kisazo chiet un,
 Pa Lal chutphah ang a ding di'n.</lyrics>
</song>